snippet.title: High Above - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to your Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3535760/High_Above/

High Above is a small rooftop-building game about finding peace in the skies. Design and grow your perfect rooftop retreat, from vibrant Cuban courtyards to modern urban hideaways. Watch the world come to life around you, at your own pace, in your own little oasis.

No timers. No stress. Just your own quiet corner in the clouds.

Created by: DVision Games
Published by: UNIKAT Label
